<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Dashboard - CineBook</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #f84464;
            --secondary: #222;
            --background: #0f0f0f;
            --text: #fff;
            --text-secondary: #aaa;
            --card-bg: #222;
            --card-hover: #2a2a2a;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .navbar {
            background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.95);
            padding: 15px 0;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo::before {
            content: "";
            display: inline-block;
            width: 10px;
            height: 24px;
            background: var(--primary);
            margin-right: 10px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text);
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--primary);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .nav-links a.active {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .nav-links a.active::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 100px 20px 40px;
        }

        .admin-header {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .admin-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .admin-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 70px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .stats-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(34, 34, 34, 0.5);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary) 0%, #ff8f70 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .stat-label {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .card-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .admin-card {
            background: rgba(34, 34, 34, 0.5);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .admin-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .admin-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 5px;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--primary);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .admin-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .card-description {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .card-icon {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: rgba(248, 68, 100, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .admin-card:hover .card-icon {
            background: rgba(248, 68, 100, 0.2);
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .card-icon svg {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            fill: var(--primary);
        }

        .card-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(248, 68, 100, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .card-link:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(248, 68, 100, 0.4);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .stats-row {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .admin-title {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            
            .card-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .stat-value {
                font-size: 30px;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .stats-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .admin-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-content">
            <a href="/" class="logo">CineBook</a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/movies">Movies</a>
                <a href="/bookings">My Bookings</a>
                <a href="/admin" class="active">Admin</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="admin-header">
            <h1 class="admin-title">Admin Dashboard</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-row">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value">{{.TotalMovies}}</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Total Movies</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value">{{.TotalShowtimes}}</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Active Showtimes</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value">{{.TotalBookings}}</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Total Bookings</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value">â‚¹{{.TotalRevenue}}</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Total Revenue</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="admin-card">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M12 2c5.52 0 10 4.48 10 10s-4.48 10-10 10S2 17.52 2 12 6.48 2 12 2zm0 18c4.42 0 8-3.58 8-8s-3.58-8-8-8-8 3.58-8 8 3.58 8 8 8zm-1-13h2v6h-2zm0 8h2v2h-2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="card-title">Manage Movies</h2>
                <p class="card-description">Add, edit, or delete movies from the database with details like title, description, duration, and more.</p>
                <a href="/admin/movie/add" class="card-link">Add Movie</a>
            </div>

            <div class="admin-card">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M19 3h-4.18C14.4 1.84 13.3 1 12 1c-1.3 0-2.4.84-2.82 2H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 0c.55 0 1 .45 1 1s-.45 1-1 1-1-.45-1-1 .45-1 1-1zm-2 14l-4-4 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l6.59-6.59L18 9l-8 8z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="card-title">Manage Showtimes</h2>
                <p class="card-description">Schedule and organize movie showtimes, including date, time, theater, screen, and pricing information.</p>
                <a href="/admin/showtime/add" class="card-link">Add Showtime</a>
            </div>

            <div class="admin-card">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="card-title">View Bookings</h2>
                <p class="card-description">Review all customer bookings, track ticket sales, and analyze booking patterns to optimize your scheduling.</p>
                <a href="/bookings" class="card-link">Manage Bookings</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 